 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003E3scale provides Free \u0026amp; Enterprise API management solutions for developers, and companies to securely distribute, control, manage, operate and monetize their API to 3rd parties (e.g. developers, business partners, etc).\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003E3scale API management platform is Plug and Play, configurable, flexible and scalable and brings API providers an unparalleled level of ownership, control and configuration to ensure QoS, SLA and a great user experience.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003E3scale powers 180+ APIs and has over 85,000 developers writing applications using these APIs. 3scale customers (http://www.3scale.net/our-customers) range from Startups up to Fortune 500 companies. For example: 1WorldSync, Johnson Controls, FlightStats, Skype, Wine.com, Viadeo, Maxdome, Transport For London (TFL), Musixmatch, Peoplebrwosr, FullContact and many more. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003E3scale has offices in San Francisco, USA and Barcelona, Spain. For more information on 3scale, visit: www.3scale.net.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003E3scale\u0026#8217;s API Management solution includes the following features:\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAPI Access control and management\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAPI Traffic Monitoring and Analytics\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EDeveloper/Partner portal\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EBilling and Payments management\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EPolicy Management (Setting up of tiers, rate limits, pricing rules, etc)\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAutomatic provisioning of API access\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E",
